MPath

    store paths as parts

create Path class

    all mpaths should be Path instances

    allows for easy addition of path powers

        mpath["path"].exists()
                     .isFile()
                     .isDir()
                     .inP4()
                     .opened() -> [], [sdas, nnacu]
                     .openedBy("sdas") -> False
                     .lastEdited()

        should also work on dot enabled syntax

            mpath.path.exists()
            etc

helps for everything

    tabs unsupported (but probably work)
    no backslashes

